{"tid":1842661,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"今晚會展大會堂有CCTVB維穩新年Show,有撐警楊明，譚伯","createTime":"2020-01-25T22:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T12:35:40.000Z","uid":17646,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"6986e8416ff5399587b03e9e2d8936c7a36556be","tid":1842661,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T22:11:13.000Z","msg":"日期：2020/01/26<br />\n時間：7點訪問，8點半直播<br />\n地點：會展3樓大會堂<br />\n偽人：鄧梓峰，朱凱婷，胡楓，安德尊，譚詠麟，鍾鎮濤，草蜢，梁漢文，周柏豪，張韶涵，廖昌永，哈<br />\n喻越越，莫草倫，王冰冰，陳倩倩，陳豪，王浩信，唐詩詠，陳敏之，楊明<br />\n<br />\n會展今晚只開放舊翼比人登記左先可以入去<br />\n大家可以係門口歡迎班撐警人士<br />\n贊助維穩show嘅係世茂集團，呢排係咁落廣告打飛機<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">親生偽人收入公司有錢分<br />\n記得嚟支持喇！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n幫手推po呀<br />\n嚟到嘅就喺呢個Group講聲：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2cctvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2cctvb&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=1832a348\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2cctvb</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n－－－－－－－ <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請即follow:</span></strong> <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=2bb6b41f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb <br />\nTG 抵制TVB戰線 - 綜合狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=6fce525b\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 狙擊TVB戰士行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2cctvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2cctvb&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=1832a348\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2cctvb</a>"},{"pid":"3bb53e321